[
    {
        "text": "There are many ways to deal with a close-minded boss.",
        "startTime": 777,
        "endTime": 3319,
        "slowStartTime": 1315,
        "slowEndTime": 5203
    },
    {
        "text": "Some are right and some are simply wrong.",
        "startTime": 3599,
        "endTime": 6120,
        "slowStartTime": 5549,
        "slowEndTime": 9405
    },
    {
        "text": "Here are three things you should avoid doing.",
        "startTime": 6902,
        "endTime": 8974,
        "slowStartTime": 10503,
        "slowEndTime": 13686
    },
    {
        "text": "Number one: Don't ignore your boss as this will only emphasize a lack of interest and respect...",
        "startTime": 9406,
        "endTime": 14625,
        "slowStartTime": 14259,
        "slowEndTime": 22163
    },
    {
        "text": "...and will ultimately create a gap between the two of you.",
        "startTime": 14864,
        "endTime": 17236,
        "slowStartTime": 22446,
        "slowEndTime": 26079
    },
    {
        "text": "Number two: Don't push your point of view with aggression...",
        "startTime": 17682,
        "endTime": 20755,
        "slowStartTime": 26673,
        "slowEndTime": 31358
    },
    {
        "text": "...as this will only put your boss in a defensive state,...",
        "startTime": 20967,
        "endTime": 23479,
        "slowStartTime": 31601,
        "slowEndTime": 35444
    },
    {
        "text": "...and he will less likely be open to your ideas.",
        "startTime": 23818,
        "endTime": 26223,
        "slowStartTime": 35877,
        "slowEndTime": 39559
    },
    {
        "text": "Number three: Don't try to prove that you are better than your boss.",
        "startTime": 26619,
        "endTime": 29962,
        "slowStartTime": 40079,
        "slowEndTime": 45168
    },
    {
        "text": "This is counterproductive and will leave your boss feeling inadequate.",
        "startTime": 30223,
        "endTime": 33875,
        "slowStartTime": 45484,
        "slowEndTime": 51038
    },
    {
        "text": "Instead, think about these three suggestions.",
        "startTime": 34479,
        "endTime": 37771,
        "slowStartTime": 51869,
        "slowEndTime": 56882
    },
    {
        "text": "Number one: Consider the fact that you may be wrong.",
        "startTime": 37988,
        "endTime": 40678,
        "slowStartTime": 57132,
        "slowEndTime": 61242
    },
    {
        "text": "Take the time to reflect on your thoughts and find middle ground.",
        "startTime": 41038,
        "endTime": 44519,
        "slowStartTime": 61707,
        "slowEndTime": 67004
    },
    {
        "text": "Number two: Patience goes a long way.",
        "startTime": 45033,
        "endTime": 47931,
        "slowStartTime": 67700,
        "slowEndTime": 72122
    },
    {
        "text": "So, keep that smile on your face and be cool.",
        "startTime": 48379,
        "endTime": 50873,
        "slowStartTime": 72719,
        "slowEndTime": 76534
    },
    {
        "text": "And finally, incorporate your ideas with your boss' ideas.",
        "startTime": 51489,
        "endTime": 55075,
        "slowStartTime": 77384,
        "slowEndTime": 82837
    },
    {
        "text": "This way, both of you can eventually come together and agree.",
        "startTime": 55388,
        "endTime": 58592,
        "slowStartTime": 83232,
        "slowEndTime": 88113
    },
    {
        "text": "Never stop pursuing common ground...",
        "startTime": 58975,
        "endTime": 60901,
        "slowStartTime": 88613,
        "slowEndTime": 91576
    },
    {
        "text": "...as this can be the foundation for a better relationship.",
        "startTime": 61183,
        "endTime": 63956,
        "slowStartTime": 91925,
        "slowEndTime": 96159
    },
    {
        "text": "How have you dealt with a close-minded boss in the past?",
        "startTime": 64302,
        "endTime": 66830,
        "slowStartTime": 96603,
        "slowEndTime": 100470
    },
    {
        "text": "Feel free to share some of your experiences below.",
